<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Acceptance Letter - ICCA</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f7f9fc;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      max-width: 720px;
      width: 90%;
      padding: 60px 50px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-align: left;
      border: 1px solid #dce3ea;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #1f2e4c;
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .highlight {
      color: #004085;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    p {
      color: #2b2b2b;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 17px;
      margin: 12px 0;
    }

    .signature {
      margin-top: 55px;
    }

    .signature p {
      margin: 3px 0;
      color: #3a3a3a;
    }

    .date {
      text-align: right;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #888;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        padding: 40px 25px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Acceptance Notification - <span class="highlight">ICCA 2025</span></h1>
    <p>
      Dear <strong>Ayoub</strong>,
    </p>
    <p>
      We are pleased to inform you that you have been <strong>officially accepted into the 2025 ICCA Program</strong>.
      Your application demonstrated a clear passion for programming and a commitment to excellence that impressed our admissions panel.
    </p>
    <p>
      As a member of the ICCA (International Code & Computing Association), you will have access to exclusive mentorship sessions, development challenges, and a vibrant community of like-minded innovators.
    </p>
    <p>
      Additional details regarding your onboarding and program access will be shared with you via email.
    </p>
    <p>
      We look forward to witnessing your contributions and progress throughout the program.
    </p>
    <div class="signature">
      <p>Sincerely,</p>
      <p><strong>Sarah El-Houari</strong></p>
      <p>Director of Admissions</p>
      <p>International Code & Computing Association (ICCA)</p>
    </div>
    <div class="date">Issued: July 29, 2025</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
